STATE
v.
DaQuan Antonio GREEN 162P19-1 Supreme Court of North Carolina. May 3, 2019 DaQuan Antonio Green, for Green, DaQuan. Daniel P. O'Brien, Special Deputy Attorney General, James R. O'Neill, District Attorney, for State of N.C.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 31st of December 2018 by Defendant for Petition Regarding Violation of Constitutional Rights:

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 3rd of May 2019."
